<div class="about-container">
  <h2>About TodoWebApp</h2>
  <p>
    TodoWebApp is an open-source task management application designed to help
    individuals and teams stay organized and productive. Whether you're working
    on personal projects, collaborating with a group, or simply managing your
    daily tasks, TodoWebApp simplifies the process.
  </p>

  <h3>Key Features</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Easy task creation, editing, and deletion</li>
    <li>Task prioritization and due dates</li>
    <li>Support for multiple task lists and categories</li>
    <li>User-friendly interface with real-time updates</li>
  </ul>

  <p>
    Built with Node.js and MongoDB, TodoWebApp offers a secure and scalable
    solution for task management. Our mission is to provide a platform that
    enhances productivity and encourages efficient task completion.
  </p>

  <h3>Join Us for Hacktoberfest!</h3>
  <p>
    <strong
      >TodoWebApp is open-source and welcomes contributions from developers of
      all skill levels.</strong
    >
    Hacktoberfest is the perfect opportunity to get involved. Whether you're
    interested in fixing bugs, adding new features, improving the user
    interface, or simply enhancing the documentation, your contributions are
    valued.
  </p>

  <p>
    Start your journey with us, learn from experienced developers, and make a
    meaningful impact on an open-source project. Join the TodoWebApp community
    for a rewarding Hacktoberfest experience!
  </p>
</div>

